      | exclusivity      | 2         |
      | studentid[0]     | Student 1 |
    And I click on "Add another student" "button"
    And I set the following fields to these values:
      | studentid[1]     | Student 2 |
    And I click on "Add another student" "button"
    And I set the following fields to these values:
      | studentid[2]     | Student 3 |
